external_knowledge:
- Mental health scores and support scores are calculated based on the sum of responses to relevant survey questions; 
- The scores and ranks provide insight into employee well-being and support within the organization; 
- Departments and positions with lower average scores may require additional support or resources to improve employee mental health and overall job satisfaction.

sql:
SELECT DISTINCT department, position
FROM employees
ORDER BY department, position;

SELECT employee_id, survey_date
FROM survey_responses
ORDER BY survey_date DESC;
